i Beauty could adopt.", "relevance": "benchmark opportunity"}, {"brand": "La Beauté Louis Vuitton", "event_type": "launch", "headline": "Louis Vuitton expands La Beauté with LV Crayon, a monogram-shaped lip liner by Pat McGrath in ten shades", "summary": "La Beauté Louis Vuitton introduced its first dedicated lip liner, the LV Crayon, created under Dame Pat McGrath with a monogram-flower form designed by Konstantin Grcic and ten shades running from Beige Atlas to Monogram Rouge. The launch ships with an ecosystem of accessories including a lip blending brush, a beauty sharpener and a Monogram canvas pencil case.", "url": "https://whitewall.art/lifestyle/where-every-line-begins-louis-vuitton-unveils-the-luxury-lv-crayon-by-dame-pat-mcgrath/", "source": "Whitewall", "tier": "T2", "published_at": "2026-06-26", "why_it_matters": "루이비통이 출시 1년 만에 립스틱, 밤에 이어 립 라이너까지 색조 라인을 빠르게 넓히며 최고가 뷰티 시장을 선점하고 있어, 구찌 뷰티의 색조 확장 속도가 상대적으로 느려 보일 위험이 있다.", "why_it_matters_en": "Louis Vuitton's rapid category build-out under Pat McGrath keeps raising the bar for couture-house makeup; Gucci Beauty's slower color expansion risks looking a step behind.", "relevance": "competitive threat"}, {"brand": "La Beauté Louis Vuitton", "event_type": "trend", "headline": "Louis Vuitton frames makeup as collectible hard luxury, anchored by a 400-euro sharpener ecosystem", "summary": "Coverage of the LV Crayon launch stresses Louis Vuitton's strategy of selling beauty as collectible objects — including a 400-euro Konstantin Grcic-designed sharpener — meant to be cherished, displayed and handed down like a handbag rather than used up and discarded. The approach signals an ambition to lift cosmetics to the status of leather goods.", "url": "https://www.thearcadiaonline.com/louis-vuitton-makes-its-next-beauty-move-with-lv-crayon-a-collectible-lip-liner-designed-by-dame-pat-mcgrath/", "source": "The Arcadia Online", "tier": "T2", "published_at": "2026-06-25", "why_it_matters": "루이비통은 화장품을 가방처럼 소장하는 물건으로 격상시켜 가격