rmes.com/en/"}, {"brand": "Hermes", "event_type": "pricing_signal", "headline": "Hermes 2026 Birkin and Kelly price increases confirmed as significant year-on-year jump", "summary": "Multiple secondary-market and enthusiast sources have confirmed that Hermes implemented a notable price increase on its Birkin and Kelly bags in January 2026, continuing the brand's policy of systematic annual list-price escalation to defend exclusivity and support resale value.", "significance": "medium", "source": "BagUSeek", "tier": "T2", "published_at": "2026-01", "why_it_matters": "에르메스의 지속적 가격 인상 정책은 초고가 가방 시장의 가격 리더십을 공고히 하며, 구찌가 엔트리 럭셔리와 하이 럭셔리 가격대 전략을 재조정할 때 시장 기준선 역할을 함.", "why_it_matters_en": "Hermes's consistent price escalation on icon bags reinforces its price-leadership position in ultra-premium leather goods and sets the ceiling against which Gucci's own pricing architecture should be benchmarked.", "relevance_tag": "competitive threat", "url": "https://baguseek.com/complete-guide-hermes-january-2026-bag-price-increase"}, {"brand": "Hermes", "event_type": "runway_show", "headline": "Hermes FW 2026 womenswear — nocturnal elegance, completed March 2026", "url": "https://www.whowhatwear.com/fashion/runway/hermes-paris-fashion-week-fall-winter-2026", "source": "Who What Wear", "tier": "T2", "published_at": "2026-03", "why_it_matters": "에르메스 FW 2026 여성복은 나데주 반헤의 감각적 방향성을 확인시키며, 조용한 럭셔리 미학이 시즌을 지배하는 트렌드를 강화함.", "why_it_matters_en": "Hermes FW 2026 womenswear confirmed Nadege Vanhee's sensual quiet-luxury direction, reinforcing the dominant aesthetic that Gucci must either complement or differentiate against.", "relevance_tag": "category trend"}, {"brand": "Chanel", "event_type": "runway_show", "headline": "Chanel Haute Couture SS 2026 presented under Matthieu Blazy", "url": "https://www.fhcm.paris/en/collection/chanel-haute-couture-springsummer-2026", "source": "FHCM", "tier": "T1", "published_at": "2026-07", "why_it_matters": "블라지 체제 첫 오뜨 꾸튀르 컬렉션은 샤넬의 쿠튀르 헤리티지를 현대적으로 재정의하는 시금